Company Info Finder
Company Info Finder is a simple Chrome browser extension that allows users to quickly search for comprehensive information about various companies with just a single click. This tool is ideal for researchers, business professionals, and anyone who needs quick access to company data.

Features
One-Click Search: Quickly search for company information from multiple sources in one click.
Customizable Search Options: Choose which sources to include in your search.
User-Friendly Interface: Simple and intuitive interface for easy use.
Lightweight and Fast: Minimal impact on browser performance.

Installation
Download the Extension: Clone or download the repository from GitHub.
Enable Developer Mode: Toggle the switch in the top-right corner of the page to enable Developer Mode.
Load Unpacked Extension: Click the "Load unpacked" button and select the folder where you downloaded or cloned the extension.
Pin the Extension: Click on the puzzle icon in the top-right corner of Chrome, find "Company Info Finder," and pin it for easy access.

Usage
Open the Extension: Click on the "Company Search" icon in your Chrome toolbar.
Enter Company Name: Type the name of the company you want to search for.
Search: CLick on "Full Search" or "Social Media Search" basde on your needs.

